      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. While the protocol is standardized and reproducible, only one test condition was evaluated, limiting coverage of the COU envelope. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this gap is accepted given that the ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard and no alternative configurations are required for 510(k) submission."
